# BrainScraper.io — System Overview

## What it is
A lead generation and enrichment platform that:
- Scrapes leads from LinkedIn Sales Navigator and Facebook
- Enriches leads with contact info, demographics, and business data
- Scrubs leads against DNC (Do Not Call) lists
- Manages and exports enriched lead data

## Core Workflow

### 1. Lead Scraping Phase
- **LinkedIn Sales Navigator**: search people/companies with filters (location, job title, company size, etc.)
- **Facebook**: discover and scrape Facebook pages/groups
- **Results**: raw lead data (name, title, company, location, LinkedIn URL)

### 2. Lead Enrichment Phase
Multi-step pipeline that adds:
- Phone numbers (via skip-tracing APIs)
- Email addresses (via skip-tracing/website extraction)
- Age/DOB (via skip-tracing)
- Zip codes (via geo database lookup)
- Income data (by zip code)
- Phone carrier info (Telnyx lookup)
- LinkedIn profile data
- Company information
- Website contacts

### 3. DNC Scrubbing Phase
- Checks phone numbers against USHA DNC database
- Marks leads as YES/NO/UNKNOWN for DNC status
- Prevents calling DNC numbers

### 4. Data Management Phase
- Saves enriched leads to `enriched-all-leads.json`
- Aggregates all leads in one place
- Provides `/enriched` page to view/manage leads
- Export to CSV functionality

## Architecture Components

### Frontend (Next.js/React)
- `LinkedInLeadGenerator.tsx` — main scraping interface
- `FacebookLeadGenerator.tsx` — Facebook scraping
- `enriched/page.tsx` — enriched leads viewer
- `settings/page.tsx` — configuration
- `BackgroundJobs.tsx` — job monitoring widget

### Backend APIs (Next.js API Routes)
- `/api/linkedin-sales-navigator` — LinkedIn search
- `/api/jobs/enrich` — trigger enrichment jobs
- `/api/jobs/scrape` — trigger scraping jobs
- `/api/load-enriched-results` — load saved leads
- `/api/aggregate-enriched-leads` — aggregate leads
- `/api/usha/scrub-*` — DNC scrubbing
- 30+ other API endpoints for enrichment services

### Background Jobs (Inngest)
- Background enrichment (non-blocking)
- Background scraping (multi-page)
- Job status tracking
- Automatic retries

### Data Storage
- `data/enriched-all-leads.json` — master lead database
- `data/enriched-leads/` — individual lead files
- `data/api-results/` — raw scraped data
- `data/jobs/` — job status files
- Railway persistent volume for production

### Data Protection System
- `leadDataManager.ts` — single entry point for all writes
- Idempotency (safe retries)
- Checksum verification
- Automatic orphan recovery
- File locking (prevents data corruption)

